+Kungani unyaka uqala ngo-equinox yasekwindla?
+-------------------------------------------------
+Ngokuhlukile nekhalenda elijwayelekile elikhombisa unyaka oqala ngoJanuwari 1, unyaka wezinkanyezi kuleli hola uqala ngesikhathi iLanga ligqema umugqa wokuzungeza kwesibhakabhaka — equinox yasekwindla. Lesi sikhathi siyiphuzu lemvelo lezero ngemijikelezo yezinkanyezi, ngoba sikwenza ukuqala "kwe-solar year cycle" futhi kamuva kakhulu sikhombisa ukuguqulwa kwangempela ebudeni bosuku nobusuku. Lesi yisikhathi lapho usuku nobusuku belingana khona ubukhulu, okwenza kube yiphuzu lokuqala lomhlaba wonke lokulinganisa isikhathi.
