+Isikhashana phakathi kwama-equinox amabili alandelana asekwindla **simele isikhathi sangempela sonyaka lwe-tropical**. Unyaka we-tropical ulingana cishe nezinsuku ezingu-365, amahora ama-5, imizuzu engu-48 nemizuzwana engu-45 — lesi yisikhathi iNhlabathi edinga sona ukuze ibuyele esimweni esifanayo eqondane neLanga, noma ukuthi equinox yasekwindla iqhubeke.
