+Olunye lomehluko obaluleke kakhulu ukuthi iWashi Lezinkanyezi **likhombisa isikhathi esifanayo sonke umuntu emhlabeni**. Isikhathi sisho somhlaba wonke ngokwemijikelezo yezinkanyezi futhi asichazwa ngezoni zesikhathi zomhlaba. Akusho lutho ukuthi ukuphi, enyakatho noma eningizimu, empumalanga noma entshonalanga, ihola likhombisa inombolo efanayo ye-Dies ne-miliDies kubo bonke abasebenzisi ngesikhathi esifanayo. Isikhathi esivamile, ngakolunye uhlangothi, sisebenzisa isikhathi somhlaba nezoni zesikhathi, ngakho isikhathi sahluka kusuka endaweni kuya endaweni, ngenkathi iWashi Lezinkanyezi lisusa lezi zinto ezahlukeneyo futhi lidala uhlelo lwesikhathi somhlaba wonke olufanayo.
