+----------------------------------
+Isikhathi esivamile siwumphumela wezivumelwano zomlando, zendawo nezomphakathi. Izoni zesikhathi zichazwa yimingcele yezombusazwe, futhi ukuqala kosuku nenyaka akuhlobene nezenzakalo zemvelo zezinkanyezi. Ngokwesibonelo, ubusuku esikhatshini esivamile asichazi sino na ezenzakalo zezinkanyezi, kepha liyiphuzu elenziwe esholiweni somhlaba. IWashi Lezinkanyezi, ngokuphambene, libopha zonke izinyunithi zalo nezikhathi zezinkanyezi ezingempela, zenza zona ingxenye yesigaba somhlaba wonke esifanele wonke umhlaba.
